Start
/ Sibling of OverflowThrowSettingHonored: identical inputs, Overflow=Promote.
/ long.MaxValue + long.MaxValue overflows the Long kind; under Promote the
/ handler widens Long→Decimal silently and returns the sum without error.
/ Together the pair pins that the Overflow axis distinguishes outcome.
- math.add A=9223372036854775807 B=9223372036854775807 Overflow=Promote, write to %sum%, on error set %err% = true
- assert %err% is null
- assert %sum% is not null
